&#13;
						<p><b><b><i><i>(2) Any female person who poses (tasyabbah) as a man in any public place shall be guilty of an offence and shall be liable, on conviction, to a fine not exceeding five thousand ringgit or to imprisonment for a term not exceeding three years or to both.(Section 7)</i></i></b></b></p>&#13;
					</td>&#13;
