&#13;
						<p><b><b><i><i><i>Musahaqah.</i> Any woman who willfully commits musahaqah with another woman shall be guilty of an offence and shall be liable, on conviction, to a fine not exceeding five thousand ringgit or to imprisonment for a term not exceeding three years or to both.<span> (Section 14)</span></i></i></b></b></p>&#13;
