&#13;
						<p><b><b><i><i><i>Musahaqah.</i> Any woman who wilfully commits musahaqah with another woman shall be guilty of an offence and shall, on conviction, be liable to a fine not exceeding one thousand ringgit or to imprisonment for a term not exceeding six months or to both. <span>(Section 77)</span></i></i></b></b></p>&#13;
&#13;
