				<p><b><b><i><i><a href="#_ftnref40" name="_ftn40" id="_ftn40"><span class="MsoFootnoteReference"><span><span class="MsoFootnoteReference"><span>[40]</span></span></span></span></a> Teh Yik Koon, <i>The Mak Nyahs: Malaysian Male to Female Transsexuals</i>, p. 72.</i></i></b></b></p>&#13;
